{"books":[{"id":"7f1148c2-92d9-4fcf-987d-99f144e1a069","name":"红旗一九六五年第十一期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/7f1148c2-92d9-4fcf-987d-99f144e1a069.pdf"],"article":{"title":"生查子·家书","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"生查子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家书[四首]"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈指渐成人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家书苣万金，四海皆昆仲。养育亦多情，形影常来梦。文武须双重。何事最关心：是否勤劳动？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春只一回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗夺如海洋，早晚云霞涌。流水片时停，毒菌争传种。转眼能抛送。百炼化为钢，只有投群众。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此墩和婚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牡丹富贵王，弹指凋尘土。岂是少扶持？不耐风和雨。何足名花数？稻麦不争芳，粒粒酬辛苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺水好行船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵观天地间，陵谷多奇趣。东海有长鲸，常与波涛伍。向下游去。若要凳英雄，先到艰难处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[四首]"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七一抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年不遇我逢辰。如此江山如此人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写就雷霆不朽文。挥将日月长明笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑荆棘等浮云。指顾崎幅成坦道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万目环球看大军。族旗猎猎春风暖，"}],"authors":["胡乔木"],"dates":[{"year":1965}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":42,"page_end":42},"tags":[{"name":"胡乔木","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}